---
import Button from './Button.astro'
import Icon from './Icon.astro'
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="badge">Early alpha - here be dragons</div>

    <h1>
      Developer tools,<br />
      without the <em>nonsense</em>
    </h1>

    <p class="subtitle">
      Analytics, translations, and more. Built because existing tools were either too expensive,
      <em>too invasive</em>, or both. Still a work in progress - but the parts that exist <em
        >actually work</em
      >.
    </p>

    <div class="values">
      <div class="value">
        <div class="value-header">
          <Icon name="coin" size={32} />
          <span class="value-label">Fairness</span>
        </div>
        <span class="value-desc"
          >Pricing matches real costs. If a feature doesn't cost more to run, it <strong
            >won't cost more to use</strong
          >.</span
        >
      </div>
      <div class="value">
        <div class="value-header">
          <Icon name="eye" size={32} />
          <span class="value-label">Honesty</span>
        </div>
        <span class="value-desc"
          >No hidden tracking, no <em>shady defaults</em>, no dark patterns. <strong
            >What you see is what you get.</strong
          ></span
        >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="actions">
      <Button href="/docs/introduction" size="large">
        <Icon name="arrow-right" size={18} />
        Get started
      </Button>
      <Button href="https://dashboard.forge.codeserk.es" variant="ghost" size="large"
        >Dashboard</Button
      >
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;

    .container {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 6rem 1.5rem 4rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 3rem;

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        gap: 2rem;
      }
    }

    .badge {
      font-size: var(--font-sm);
      color: var(--color-primary);
      border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
      padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading-no-scale);
      font-size: var(--font-6xl);
      color: var(--color-text);
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: var(--font-xl);
      color: var(--color-text-subtle);
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 560px;
    }

    .values {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      text-align: left;
      width: 100%;

      .value {
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.4rem;
        padding: 1.25rem;
        background-color: var(--color-container);
        position: relative;

        --card-color-border: var(--color-border);
        --card-color-shadow: var(--color-shadow);

        border: 4px solid var(--card-color-border);
        box-shadow: 0px 8px 0 var(--card-color-shadow);

        &::before,
        &::after {
          content: '';
          position: absolute;
          width: 10px;
          height: 10px;
          background: var(--card-color-border);
        }

        &::before {
          top: -2px;
          left: -2px;
        }

        &::after {
          bottom: -2px;
          right: -2px;
          box-shadow:
            -8px 0 0 var(--card-color-border),
            0 -8px 0 var(--card-color-border);
        }

        .value-header {
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          gap: 0.5rem;
          color: var(--color-primary);

          svg {
            fill: var(--color-primary);
            width: var(--font-2xl);
            height: var(--font-2xl);
          }
        }

        .value-label {
          font-family: var(--font-heading);
          font-size: var(--font-2xl);
          color: var(--color-primary);
        }

        .value-desc {
          font-size: var(--font-lg);
          color: var(--color-text-subtle);
          line-height: 1.6;
        }
      }
    }

    .actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
